snippet.title: RESIDENT EVIL 9: REQUIEM Leon Gameplay | Showcase Trailer
snippet.description:
Resident Evil 9: Requiem gameplay showcase trailer featuring Leon is HERE! 🔥 In this video you’ll watch the latest official gameplay reveal from the Showcase, with brand-new scenes, atmosphere, and those classic survival horror vibes that made the series legendary.

If you’re hyped for Resident Evil 9 Requiem, this is the perfect first look: Leon’s presence, the tone, the setting, the combat hints, and the kind of tension that screams “classic RE… but evolved.” 👁️🩸

✅ What you’ll find in this video

Official gameplay showcase trailer
Leon-focused moments & key scenes
New environment details, mood, and horror tone
My quick reactions + what this could mean for the story (without spoilers)

💬 Question for you, Darks:

Do you like this direction for RE9… or do you want it to go even more horror like RE7? 👇

🔔 Subscribe for more Resident Evil 9: Requiem coverage!

Expect gameplay walkthroughs, guides, bosses, secrets, story breakdowns, and the full game when it drops.

All footage belongs to its respective owners.
If you enjoyed the video, leave a like — it helps a ton! 🙌

#ResidentEvil9 #Requiem #LeonKennedy #ResidentEvil #Capcom #GameplayTrailer #Showcase #SurvivalHorror

Letra: 

RETCHÊÊÊ...

Esse é o Rap da Lealdade
Pra aquele que é fiel de fechar
Mais ou menos assim, oh

Aperta logo esse boldo 
Nós tá aqui um pelo outro
Melhor aliado 
Mermo com o tempo fechado 
Quando o calo aperta é nos que sabe 
Quem que são os de verdade 
Pra superar junto as piores fases 
Fumaça do balão sobe
De raça teu sangue é nobre (é nobre)
Tu não se rendeu pro sistema
Mesmo causando problemas  
Nunca vi ninguém com a tua dispô 
Tu transformou ódio em amor 
Vários mentiram, só tu foi  
Sincero quando eu tava errado (errado) 

(REFRÃO)

Meu parceiro, Oh meu Deus 
Nem meus defeitos fez tu me abandonar 
Armas e rosas tão na tua escolta 
A vida é mais do que nós posta, eu sei 
Foi alta a aposta
 
Abençoado, Iluminado 
Obrigado Deus eu vivo como eu quero
Baseado entrelaçado nos dedos 
Enquanto eu acelero 
De Salvador, Rio de Janeiro, São Paulo 
Deus é o 00 
Quando ninguém tava lá tu me fez acreditar, irmão 

Por isso tu merece uma canção 
Toda lealdade do meu coração 
toda minha gratidão 

(REFRÃO)

Meu parceiro, Oh meu Deus 
Nem meus defeitos fez tu me abandonar 
Armas e rosas tão na tua escolta 
A vida é mais do que nós posta, eu sei 
Foi alta a aposta
 
Se tudo acabar nós vai ta lá reinando 
Se tudo desabar nós vai ta lá zuando
Zuando o plantão
Se tudo acabar nós vai ta lá reinando 
Se tudo desabar nós vai ta lá zuando

Estúdio: NADAMAL RECORD$

snippet.title: The Sims 4: Royalty & Legacy | Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the reveal trailer for The Sims 4: Royalty & Legacy Expansion Pack*! Build a powerful Dynasty, become a Noble, avoid Scandal, and do it all for the plot. Experience storybook moments, reap the perks of Prestige, and climb your way to glory. No two paths to power are the same!

Pre-order now: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-royalty-and-legacy-grand-bundle

Learn more: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/news/royalty-and-legacy-expansion-pack

Your kingdom awaits, and it's brimming with opulence, culture, and complex relationships. The throne is empty, and only one Sim can wear the crown. Nobles might have rivals, Dynasties may have Outcasts, and anyone can find themselves at the heart of a saucy scandal. The stage is set and the stories of ascension are yours to tell.

The Sims 4: Royalty & Legacy will be available February 12, 2026 at 10am PT on EA App PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 4 (PS4), and PlayStation 5 (PS5).

*Requires The Sims 4 & all game updates. For PC, see minimum system requirements for the pack.

**CONDITIONS AND RESTRICTIONS APPLY.

snippet.title: FATAL FURY: CotW ｜ Season 2 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The legend continues to evolve.
Season 2 of FATAL FURY: City of the Wolves begins January 22!

Six characters over six months, each released monthly. Season 2 will be a season of continuous evolution.
SNK plans to release one character every month for six months in Season 2, beginning with its January 22 kickoff.In addition to the four long-awaited additions below, two mystery challengers will also join the fray. More information about their identities will be revealed in due course, so stay tuned!Experience this ever-evolving legend and the exhilarating battles within as we enter a new season!

Season 2 Characters
- KIM JAE HOON
- NIGHTMARE GEESE
- BLUE MARY
- WOLFGANG KRAUSER
- Two mystery characters (TBA)

💻Official Site 
https://www.snk-corp.co.jp/us/games/fatalfury-cotw/
📶X
https://x.com/FATALFURY_PR
📶Instagram
https://www.instagram.com/fatalfury_pr/
---------------------------------------------
伝説は進化し続ける――
『餓狼伝説 City of the Wolves』Season 2、1月22日開幕！

全6キャラクターを毎月配信。Season 2は“継続的進化”のシーズンへ
1月22日のSeason 2開幕以降、全6キャラクターを毎月1体ずつ順次配信予定。
Season 2には、シリーズファン待望の以下4キャラクターに加え、正体不明のミステリーキャラクター2体が参戦。ミステリーキャラクターについては、後日その正体が明かされるので乞うご期待！
新シーズンに突入し、更なる進化を続ける伝説のバトルを体感せよ！

＜Season 2 参戦キャラクター＞
・キム・ジェイフン
・ナイトメアギース

・ヴォルフガング・クラウザー

snippet.title: [Official Trailer] My Romance Scammer รักจริง หลังแต่ง
snippet.description:
เมื่อ ไป๋ (มาร์ค จิรันธนิน) และ นอร์ธ (ปูน มิตรภักดี)
หลานชายเจ้าสัวว่าที่เจ้าของอาณาจักรแสนล้านตระกูลจิระมงคลธนันต์
โดนสองสแกมเมอร์ อย่าง ยู (โอห์ม ฐิติวัฒน์) และ ทิม (จูเนียร์ ปณชัย)
หลอกแต่งงานเพื่อที่จะได้สินสมรสแบบมหาศาล!
        นอร์ธที่ตกลงแต่งงานกับยูอย่างลับๆ ไปแล้ว แต่เพิ่งมารู้ว่าโดนหลอก
พอจะหย่าก็หย่าไม่ได้เพราะดันยกทรัพย์สินส่วนหนึ่งให้ยูไปแล้ว!!
กระทบกับทิมที่กำลังวางแผนจัดงานแต่งกับไป๋ในไม่ช้า
แล้วทิมจะโดนจับโป๊ะว่าเป็นสแกมเมอร์มาหลอกไป๋ด้วยหรือไม่!?
        ความรักที่เริ่มต้นด้วยการหลอกครั้งนี้จะเป็นอย่างไร
มาร่วมจับโป๊ะแก๊งสแกมเมอร์พร้อมกันใน “My Romance Scammer
รักจริง หลังแต่ง” ทุกวันอาทิตย์ เวลา 20:30 น. ทางช่อง GMM25
และรับชมย้อนหลังได้ที่ WeTV ที่เดียวเท่านั้น เวลา 21:30 น. 
เริ่มตอนแรก 1 กุมภาพันธ์นี้

กำกับซีรีส์ : ศิวัจน์ สวัสดิ์มณีกุล

รายชื่อนักแสดง
จูเนียร์ ปณชัย ศรีอาริยะรุ่งเรือง รับบท ทิม
มาร์ค จิรันธนิน ตรัยรัตนยนต์ รับบท ไป๋
โอห์ม ฐิติวัฒน์ ฤทธิ์ประเสริฐ รับบท ยู
ปูน มิตรภักดี รับบท นอร์ธ
กระปุก พลอยนิรา หิรัญทวีศิลป์ รับบท นานะ
หลุยส์ ธณวิน ธีรโพสุการ รับบท เพียว
แม็ค ณัฐพัชร์ นิมจิรวัฒน์ รับบท ต้าร์ซาน
อาร์ม วีรยุทธ จันทร์สุข รับบท เปรม
ไตเติ้ล กีรติ พวงมาลี รับบท เกื้อ

▸ Inscreva-se no canal da Julia Vitória:

@JuliaVitóriaOfc apresenta Segurança Canta Minh’alma, hino 375 do Cantor Cristão. A versão em português de Blessed Assurance foi gravada ao lado de @elisoares, um dos maiores nomes do segmento, que tem diversos hits, entre eles, Me Ajude a Melhorar, Os Anjos Te Louvam e Os Sonhos de Deus.

A cantora gospel reforça que resgatar louvores antigos é algo muito importante para ela e celebra também a parceria com o vencedor de três Grammys Latinos. “Fico profundamente emocionada por ter a oportunidade de gravar ao lado desse amigo. Eli Soares carrega muito talento, criatividade e, principalmente, simplicidade”, reforça Julia, que interpreta diversos louvores de adoração como De Dentro Pra Fora, Esperança, Começo, Meio e Fim e Sem Palavras, com Luciano Camargo.

Segurança Canta Minh’alma é o sexto lançamento do DVD gravado Ao Vivo na Ópera de Arame - que conta com dez faixas, entre elas, Restaura o Teu Altar, Maravilhosa Graça, Canção dos Redimidos, com @NiveaSoaresOfficial, e os medleys João Viu / Além do Rio Azul e Amor Infinito / A Mensagem da Cruz. O projeto, registrado em 2025, conta ainda com a participação especial de @marcelomarkesoficial.

▸ Letra:

Vivo feliz, pois sou de Jesus
E já desfruto o gozo da luz
Sou por Jesus, herdeiro de Deus
Ele me leva à glória dos Céus

Canta, minha alma
Canta ao Senhor
Rende-lhe sempre ardente louvor

Sempre vivendo em Seu grande amor
Me regozijo em meu Salvador
Esperançoso, vivo na luz
Pela bondade do meu Jesus

Canta minha alma! Canta ao Senhor!
Pois Ele é bom sempre bom
E ouviu o meu clamor e Dele eu sou!

Composição – Segurança / Canta Minh’alma:

Versão: George Benjamim Nind / Ana Tristão, Rafa Ortega e Gabriel Guedes
